## 01_modus_ponens (THM)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 01 - Modus ponens (propositional)
% From  p  and  p => q,  conclude  q.   No quantifiers.
% Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(p_decl, type, p: $o ).
thf(q_decl, type, q: $o ).

thf(fact_p,  axiom, p ).
thf(rule_pq, axiom, p => q ).

thf(goal, conjecture, q ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

