## 03_existential_intro (THM)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 03 - Existential generalisation
% All humans are mortal; Socrates is human; therefore something is mortal.
% Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(human_decl,    type, human:    $i > $o ).
thf(mortal_decl,   type, mortal:   $i > $o ).
thf(socrates_decl, type, socrates: $i ).

thf(all_humans_mortal, axiom,
    ! [X: $i] : ( ( human @ X ) => ( mortal @ X ) ) ).
thf(socrates_human, axiom, human @ socrates ).

thf(goal, conjecture, ? [X: $i] : ( mortal @ X ) ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

