## 04_hypothetical_syllogism (THM)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 04 - Hypothetical syllogism (universal conclusion)
% If every p is a q and every q is an r, then every p is an r.
% Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(p_decl, type, p: $i > $o ).
thf(q_decl, type, q: $i > $o ).
thf(r_decl, type, r: $i > $o ).

thf(p_implies_q, axiom, ! [X: $i] : ( ( p @ X ) => ( q @ X ) ) ).
thf(q_implies_r, axiom, ! [X: $i] : ( ( q @ X ) => ( r @ X ) ) ).

thf(goal, conjecture, ! [X: $i] : ( ( p @ X ) => ( r @ X ) ) ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

