## 05_symmetry (THM)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 05 - Symmetric relation
% 'likes' is symmetric and alice likes bob; therefore bob likes alice.
% Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(likes_decl, type, likes: $i > $i > $o ).
thf(alice_decl, type, alice: $i ).
thf(bob_decl,   type, bob:   $i ).

thf(likes_symmetric, axiom,
    ! [X: $i, Y: $i] : ( ( likes @ X @ Y ) => ( likes @ Y @ X ) ) ).
thf(alice_likes_bob, axiom, likes @ alice @ bob ).

thf(goal, conjecture, likes @ bob @ alice ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

