## 07_equality_congruence (THM)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 07 - Equality and function congruence
% a = b, p(a), f(a) = c  =>  p(b)  and  f(b) = c   (substitution of equals).
% Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(f_decl, type, f: $i > $i ).
thf(p_decl, type, p: $i > $o ).
thf(a_decl, type, a: $i ).
thf(b_decl, type, b: $i ).
thf(c_decl, type, c: $i ).

thf(a_eq_b, axiom, a = b ).
thf(p_of_a, axiom, p @ a ).
thf(f_of_a, axiom, ( f @ a ) = c ).

thf(goal, conjecture, ( ( p @ b ) & ( ( f @ b ) = c ) ) ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

