## 11_identity_unique (TIMEOUT)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 11 - Uniqueness of the identity element
% Any two two-sided identities of a binary operation are equal.
% (No associativity needed.)   Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(mult_decl, type, mult: $i > $i > $i ).

thf(goal, conjecture,
    ! [E1: $i, E2: $i]
    : ( ( ( ! [X: $i] : ( ( ( mult @ E1 @ X ) = X ) & ( ( mult @ X @ E1 ) = X ) ) )
        & ( ! [X: $i] : ( ( ( mult @ E2 @ X ) = X ) & ( ( mult @ X @ E2 ) = X ) ) ) )
     => ( E1 = E2 ) ) ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

