## 12_baby_puzzle (THM)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 12 - "Everybody loves my baby"
% Everybody loves my baby; my baby loves nobody but me;
% therefore my baby is me.   Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(loves_decl, type, loves: $i > $i > $o ).
thf(baby_decl,  type, baby: $i ).
thf(me_decl,    type, me:   $i ).

thf(everybody_loves_baby, axiom, ! [X: $i] : ( loves @ X @ baby ) ).
thf(baby_loves_only_me,   axiom,
    ! [X: $i] : ( ( loves @ baby @ X ) => ( X = me ) ) ).

thf(goal, conjecture, baby = me ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

