## 13_injectivity (TIMEOUT)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 13 - Injectivity from a left inverse
% If g(f(x)) = x for all x, then f is injective.   Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(f_decl, type, f: $i > $i ).
thf(g_decl, type, g: $i > $i ).

thf(left_inverse, axiom, ! [X: $i] : ( ( g @ ( f @ X ) ) = X ) ).

thf(goal, conjecture,
    ! [X: $i, Y: $i] : ( ( ( f @ X ) = ( f @ Y ) ) => ( X = Y ) ) ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

