## 14_asymmetry (TIMEOUT)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 14 - Irreflexive + transitive  =>  asymmetric
% Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(r_decl, type, r: $i > $i > $o ).

thf(irreflexive, axiom, ! [X: $i] : ( ~ ( r @ X @ X ) ) ).
thf(transitive,  axiom,
    ! [X: $i, Y: $i, Z: $i] :
      ( ( ( r @ X @ Y ) & ( r @ Y @ Z ) ) => ( r @ X @ Z ) ) ).

thf(goal, conjecture,
    ! [X: $i, Y: $i] : ( ( r @ X @ Y ) => ( ~ ( r @ Y @ X ) ) ) ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

