## 16_dual_drinker (THM)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 16 - Dual drinker paradox
% There is someone such that, if they have property p, then everyone does:
%   |-  ?x. !y. ( p(x) => p(y) )
% Classical; no axioms.   Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(p_decl, type, p: $i > $o ).

thf(goal, conjecture,
    ? [X: $i] : ( ! [Y: $i] : ( ( p @ X ) => ( p @ Y ) ) ) ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

