## 17_quantifier_distribution (THM)

```elixir
{res, stats} = prove ~p"""
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
% 17 - Quantifier / disjunction distribution
%   ( !x. (p(x) | q) )  <=>  ( (!x. p(x)) | q )   where q does not depend on x.
% Status : Theorem
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
thf(p_decl, type, p: $i > $o ).
thf(q_decl, type, q: $o ).

thf(goal, conjecture,
    ( ( ! [X: $i] : ( ( p @ X ) | q ) )
  <=> ( ( ! [X: $i] : ( p @ X ) ) | q ) ) ).
%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
""", stats: true

format_result res
```

